Amen! Oh Lord, renew my mind day by day and dispense more of Your life into me. May You purify my wandering thoughts completely! Replace my will oh Lord with Your own that I would just say Amen Lord Jesus! Lord I want to always trust You and follow You! Permeate and saturate me with Your dear self! Praise the Lord!
Renew my mind, oh Lord, day by day dispense Your life;
My wandering thoughts purify completely;
Replace my will, oh Lord, with Your will that I would say
"Oh Lord, Amen," always trusting You, following You.
